content:
We've created a quote business process for Homeowners and Renters insurance. You can create new quotes from:

* OmniScript flow
* Quote object UI in the Lex console (built with Lightning Web Components)
* Policyholder Site (policyholders follow a guided flow to quickly create quotes)

You can also create an Auto, Marine or Property quote from the account page with just a few clicks.

For lines of business that need documents containing quote details, the Quote Proposal OmniScript creates such documents.
title: Property Quote Business Process for Insurance
